Text: My anti Virus interupted the Download? I run avira free, please advise me is it safe to download?
I have NOD32 and he didn`t find any virus!  It is very safe! Don`t hesitate!
It's clean. Add the torrent download directory as an exception to your Avira config, and run antivir check on downloaded files in a separate directory.
